-   <span data-ttu-id="3155f-423"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.PhonemeReached>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3155f-423"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.PhonemeReached>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3155f-424">シンセサイザーが1つの文字または文字の組み合わせに到達するたびに発生し、言語の音声を個別に発音します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3155f-424">Raised each time the synthesizer reaches a letter or combination of letters that constitute a discreet sound of speech in a language.</span></span>  
  
